      ],
      "assignee": "agent",
      "description": "Sensitivity comparison of batch-integration methods (harmony, scanorama, bbknn). The harness runs each variant; the SME selects the winner via select_sensitivity_winner before downstream clustering consumes the integrated embeddings.\n",
      "spec": {
